The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically intrinsic image decomposition, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses physically-based rendering, which falls under computer graphics, making cs.GR (Computer Graphics) the second most likely category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
